      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Stampa importo in riga                                    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       stp-imp-rig-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione numero caratteri e maschera di   *
      *              * editing                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Deviazione in funzione del numero decimali  *
      *                  * valuta                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     stp-imp-rig-100
                     stp-imp-rig-200
                     stp-imp-rig-300
                     depending            on   w-stp-imp-rig-dcv      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Numero decimali : 0                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-stp-imp-rig-imp    >    999999999 or
                     w-stp-imp-rig-imp    <   -999999999
                     move  11             to   w-stp-imp-rig-car
                     move  spaces         to   w-stp-imp-rig-edm
           else      move  09             to   w-stp-imp-rig-car
                     move  "G"            to   w-stp-imp-rig-edm      .
           go to     stp-imp-rig-500.
       stp-imp-rig-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Numero decimali : 1                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-stp-imp-rig-imp    >    99999999 or
                     w-stp-imp-rig-imp    <   -99999999
                     move  09             to   w-stp-imp-rig-car
                     move  spaces         to   w-stp-imp-rig-edm
           else      move  07             to   w-stp-imp-rig-car
                     move  "G"            to   w-stp-imp-rig-edm      .
           go to     stp-imp-rig-500.
       stp-imp-rig-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Numero decimali : 2                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-stp-imp-rig-imp    >    99999999 or
                     w-stp-imp-rig-imp    <   -99999999
                     move  08             to   w-stp-imp-rig-car
                     move  spaces         to   w-stp-imp-rig-edm
           else      move  06             to   w-stp-imp-rig-car
                     move  "G"            to   w-stp-imp-rig-edm
                     add   1              to   w-stp-imp-rig-pos      .
           go to     stp-imp-rig-500.
       stp-imp-rig-300.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Numero decimali : 3                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-stp-imp-rig-imp    >    999999999 or
                     w-stp-imp-rig-imp    <   -999999999
                     move  07             to   w-stp-imp-rig-car
                     move  spaces         to   w-stp-imp-rig-edm
           else      move  06             to   w-stp-imp-rig-car
                     move  "G"            to   w-stp-imp-rig-edm      .
           go to     stp-imp-rig-500.
       stp-imp-rig-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Stampa                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "PF"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      w-stp-imp-rig-car    to   v-car                  .
           move      w-stp-imp-rig-dcv    to   v-dec                  .
           move      "S"                  to   v-sgn                  .
           move      w-stp-imp-rig-edm    to   v-edm                  .
           move      w-stp-imp-rig-lin    to   v-lin                  .
           move      w-stp-imp-rig-pos    to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-stp-imp-rig-imp    to   v-num                  .
           if        w-stp-imp-rig-dcv    =    1
                     divide 10            into v-num
           else if   w-stp-imp-rig-dcv    =    2
                     divide 100           into v-num
           else if   w-stp-imp-rig-dcv    =    3
                     divide 1000          into v-num                  .
           if        w-stp-imp-rig-sgn    =    "-"
                     multiply -1          by   v-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       stp-imp-rig-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Interrogazione : Function-keys previste in Mark-points    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       qry-det-fky-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Function key Slct                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se non e' stata passata una variabile di i. *
      *                  * p.c. per l'ammissibilita' del tasto Slct :  *
      *                  * no function key Slct                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-ipc-snx-slc-snx    not  = "S"
                     move  spaces         to   v-pfk (01)
                     go to qry-det-fky-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se il valore della variabile di i.p.c. per  *
      *                  * l'ammissibilita' del tasto Slct e' diverso  *
      *                  * da 'S' : no function key Slct               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-ipc-snx-slc-val    not  = "S"
                     move  spaces         to   v-pfk (01)
                     go to qry-det-fky-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ammissibilita' del tasto Slct               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "SLCT"               to   v-pfk (01)             .
       qry-det-fky-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Function key Expd                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "EXPD"               to   v-pfk (02)             .
       qry-det-fky-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Altre function keys                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   v-pfk (03)             .
           move      spaces               to   v-pfk (04)             .
           move      spaces               to   v-pfk (05)             .
           move      spaces               to   v-pfk (06)             .
           move      spaces               to   v-pfk (07)             .
           move      spaces               to   v-pfk (08)             .
           move      spaces               to   v-pfk (09)             .
           move      spaces               to   v-pfk (10)             .
       qry-det-fky-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Interrogazione : Trattamento Function-key selezionata     *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       qry-trt-fun-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione flag di interruzione forzata    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-qry-flg-int      .
       qry-trt-fun-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione a seconda della function-key         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "SLCT"
                     go to qry-trt-fun-200
           else if   v-key                =    "EXPD"
                     go to qry-trt-fun-300
           else      go to qry-trt-fun-900.
       qry-trt-fun-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se function-key Slct                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione function key                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   v-key                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Bufferizzazione contenuto del mark-point    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      v-cnt                to   w-mpn                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Scrittura della variabile 'dat-doc' per il  *
      *                  * livello di profondita' precedente o per lo  *
      *                  * stesso livello di profondita' applicativa a *
      *                  * seconda se il sottoprogramma e' stato ri-   *
      *                  * chiamato dal main oppure da un sottopro-    *
      *                  * gramma dello stesso livello                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "PV"                 to   s-ope                  .
           move      "dat-doc"            to   s-var                  .
           if        w-ipc-tdc-mos-snx    =    "S" and
                     w-ipc-tdc-mos-val    =    "M"
                     move  "-"            to   s-dop
           else      move  "="            to   s-dop                  .
           move      "D"                  to   s-tip                  .
           move      w-mpn-dat-doc        to   s-dat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Scrittura della variabile 'num-doc' per il  *
      *                  * livello di profondita' precedente o per lo  *
      *                  * stesso livello di profondita' applicativa a *
      *                  * seconda se il sottoprogramma e' stato ri-   *
      *                  * chiamato dal main oppure da un sottopro-    *
      *                  * gramma dello stesso livello                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "PV"                 to   s-ope                  .
           move      "num-doc"            to   s-var                  .
           if        w-ipc-tdc-mos-snx    =    "S" and
                     w-ipc-tdc-mos-val    =    "M"
                     move  "-"            to   s-dop
           else      move  "="            to   s-dop                  .
           move      "N"                  to   s-tip                  .
           move      11                   to   s-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   s-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   s-sgn                  .
           move      w-mpn-num-doc        to   s-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Scrittura della variabile 'cod-tmo' per il  *
      *                  * livello di profondita' precedente o per lo  *
      *                  * stesso livello di profondita' applicativa a *
      *                  * seconda se il sottoprogramma e' stato ri-   *
      *                  * chiamato dal main oppure da un sottopro-    *
      *                  * gramma dello stesso livello                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "PV"                 to   s-ope                  .
