      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione work area                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-let-arc-zoc-des      .
       let-arc-zoc-600.
           move      zero                 to   w-let-arc-zoc-ord      .
           move      spaces               to   w-let-arc-zoc-sgl      .
           move      spaces               to   w-let-arc-zoc-tvd      .
